dpm.content.state
Class DesignEntityStateChanger

java.lang.Object
  dpm.content.state.DesignEntityStateChanger
public class DesignEntityStateChanger
extends java.lang.Object

Sees whether a design entity's state can be changed, given available inputs. If so, it creates a new taskState advertisement and publishes it.
